Architecture:
1. Identified problem in India
2. Collected datasets related to it. 
	1. eight class science govt text book that is used across india by all central schools
	2. Ayurveda home remedies
	3. rice diseases, symptoms and management
	4. Depression, reasons, how to handle
	5. Govt reelased instructions for disaster management
3. Extracted structure from the datasets using pymupdf
4. Setup gemma 3n 4b model locally using ollama
5. Generated 2630 Q&A from strtucuted data for all datasets/domains using ollama api gemma & python
6. Trained gemma 3n 4b model on kaggle with 2630, finetuning
7. Converted model to gguf format and downloaded it locally
8. Deployed finetuned model into Ollama
9. Built a rag on structured data using FAISS, built index and saved it locally
10. Built a streamlit app for end users (family)
